@startuml consultarListaAlumnos
title Diagrama de Secuencia - Consultar Lista Alumnos (Diseño)

actor "Profesor" as Teacher
participant "Frontend (Vue)" as FE
participant "GrupoController" as Controller
participant "GrupoService" as Service
participant "AlumnoRepository" as Repository

Teacher -> FE: Ver Alumnos del Grupo
activate FE

FE -> Controller: GET /api/grupos/{grupoId}/alumnos
activate Controller

Controller -> Service: listarAlumnosPorGrupo(grupoId)
activate Service
Service -> Repository: findByGrupoId(grupoId)
activate Repository
Repository --> Service: List<Alumno>
deactivate Repository
Service --> Controller: List<AlumnoDTO>
deactivate Service

Controller --> FE: 200 OK
deactivate Controller
deactivate FE
@enduml